query_text: Which customers have placed more than 3 orders?
sql_generated:
SELECT
  c.customer_id,
  c.first_name,
  c.last_name
FROM customers AS c
JOIN orders AS o
  ON c.customer_id = o.customer_id
GROUP BY
  c.customer_id,
  c.first_name,
  c.last_name
HAVING
  COUNT(o.order_id) > 3
LIMIT 100;

query_text: Find customers who only buy from specific categories
sql_generated:
SELECT
  c.customer_id,
  c.first_name,
  c.last_name
FROM customers AS c
JOIN orders AS o
  ON c.customer_id = o.customer_id
JOIN order_items AS oi
  ON o.order_id = oi.order_id
JOIN products AS p
  ON oi.product_id = p.product_id
JOIN categories AS cat
  ON p.category = cat.category_name
GROUP BY
  c.customer_id,
  c.first_name,
  c.last_name
HAVING
  COUNT(DISTINCT cat.category_name) = 1
LIMIT 100;

query_text: Show me the top 5 best-selling products
sql_generated:
SELECT
  p.product_name,
  SUM(oi.quantity) AS total_quantity_sold
FROM products AS p
JOIN order_items AS oi
  ON p.product_id = oi.product_id
GROUP BY
  p.product_name
ORDER BY
  total_quantity_sold DESC
LIMIT 5;

query_text: Show me supplier performance by country
sql_generated:
SELECT
  s.country,
  s.supplier_name,
  SUM(oi.quantity * oi.unit_price) AS total_sales
FROM suppliers AS s
JOIN products AS p
  ON s.supplier_id = p.supplier_id
JOIN order_items AS oi
  ON p.product_id = oi.product_id
GROUP BY
  s.country,
  s.supplier_name
ORDER BY
  s.country,
  total_sales DESC
LIMIT 100
